00:14:44.175 --> 00:14:45.218
ano?

00:14:45.760 --> 00:14:47.720
[♪ mabagsik, mapanglaw na musikang tumutugtog]

00:14:53.434 --> 00:14:54.435
Halika na.

00:14:55.770 --> 00:14:57.647
Alam naman nating lahat ang kwento di ba?

00:14:57.730 --> 00:14:59.857
Hindi naman talaga dapat bawal
sa pamilya.

00:15:02.568 --> 00:15:05.822
Wooju, hindi ko sinusubukang sirain ka.

00:15:06.781 --> 00:15:08.241
-Ayos lang ako.
